s/2018/12/clients-1024x597.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"321\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-433\" />We recognize that leaders today require unique skill sets to navigate industry challenges with fewer resources while also driving growth.  We also understand the value of time and are uniquely positioned, with our history of performance, to provide the solutions our clients need, on time and under budget.  \r\n\r\nMoffitt provides you with a range of solutions designed to help you advance your mission.  We offer strategic executive search services, interim solutions and management, leadership training as well as succession planning.\r\n\r\nOur construction division is comprised of dedicated consultants and support staff solely committed to the construction industry.  Their industry experience and specialization will help you identify internal and external candidates that meet and exceed expectations.  Each consultants ability to provide these services is further enhanced by market segment expertise and regional focus.\r\n\r\nWhether its managing and retaining existing talent or attracting the expertise you need, we are the partner of choice for hundreds of domestic and international clients.\r\n\r\n<a class=\"moffitt-body-button\" style=\"color: #445faa;\" href=\"http://absdsgn.com/dev/moffitt/?page_id=15\">Get started</a>','Construction Group','','inherit','closed','closed','','260-revision-v1','','','2018-12-28 23:50:33','2018-12-28 23:50:33','',260,'http://absdsgn.com/dev/moffitt/?p=436',0,'revision','',0),(437,1,'2018-12-28 23:51:53','2018-12-28 23:51:53','','candidates','','inherit','closed','closed','','candidates-2','','','2018-12-28 23:51:53','2018-12-28 23:51:53','',13,'http://absdsgn.com/dev/moffitt/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/candidates.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(438,1,'2018-12-28 23:52:13','2018-12-28 23:52:13','<h3>To Our Candidates</h3>\r\n<p>We believe that your experience with Moffitt will be the most satisfying and rewarding of any experience that you will have with an executive search and management consulting firm.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"http://absdsgn.com/dev/moffitt/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/candidates-1024x512.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"263\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-437\" />First and foremost, our consultants are professionals.  This professionalism exhibits itself in our conduct, in our attention to detail and in our follow-up.  We encourage you to get to really know your consultant.  You will see the caliber of our professional who will be advising you in what is often one of the most important decisions you will ever make.\r\n\r\nSecondly, we represent some outstanding and dynamic clients.  We thoroughly vet our clients to insure that your investment in time is worthwhile. \r\n\r\nLastly, you will receive excellent career counseling.  Based on our interview with you and our reference checks, we will be able to give you an objective, third party analysis of your current career track and future possibilities.  We will advise you of your strengths and also of areas which need improvement.  Our motto, Hire. Integrity. means a great deal to our firm and our consultants.  Making sure that you join the right organization at the right time is of paramount importance.  You will find our counseling beneficial in your lifelong career progression.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Your Expectations of Us</h3>\r\nOf course, there are certain expectations which candidates my have of Moffitt.  These include the following:\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">W</span>e will treat your resume confidentially.  It will not be sent to a client unless we have discussed the assignment with you.  Most of our candidates are not actively on the market, however, they have chosen to be present in our files so that we may monitor their careers.  Our confidentiality assures them that their current position will not be compromised.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">W</span>e will treat you with respect.  Ninety-five percent of our serious candidates accept a job offer from our clients, which we believe says something about our ability to match clients and candidates.  However, if you are made an offer and choose to decline, we will respect your decision.  We may offer our viewpoint, but we will not attempt to make something happen that could ultimately fail.  You may always be assured of our positive wished for you and your future.  Your candidacy will remain intact for future assignments where we are engaged.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">W</span>e will communicate with you often.  As we are advised of new information, we will offer you immediate feedback.  In an error of unified communications, we ask that you take our calls and/or return our messages.  Other forms of communication are too one dimensional to convey certain things.  Additionally, you may also feel free to call us after business hours if necessary.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">R</span>emember, there can only be one successful candidate for a position.  If you are not selected as a candidate for one assignment, it will not impair your candidacy for others.  In most cases, candidates are not selected because they are unqualified, there are simply other candidates that are better qualified.  You may be disappointed, but the next assignment could be the better opportunity for you.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">A</span>s an employer paid firm, all of our fees and expenses are borne by our clients.  There is never any fee or financial obligation on your part.\r\n\r\n<h3>Our Expectations of You</h3>\r\nAt Moffitt, we have certain expectations of you, the Candidate, which must be met if the search process is to work effectively.  These include the following:\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">W</span>henever you communicate with our client, call our consultant immediately and inform him or her of the conversation so that we may expedite the search process.  Duplication of efforts can create confusion among the parties.  As the professional(s) involved, the more timely the information, the more effective we can be.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">P</span>leave be honest with us as to any negative information about you personally and/or professionally that may or may not impact your career progression.  This also applies to your overall management style within your current or previous organizations.  If we are aware of these matters, we can review these with our client(s) at the beginning of the process to determine their relevancy, if any.  However, if the negatives surface later, integrity rather than relevancy becomes the issue.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">Y</span>our travel expenses for interviews will be reimbursed to your directly by our clients.  Please submit them to us for review.  We will then forward the expense to the client for expedited reimbursement.  Making us aware of said expenses will allow us to monitor their timely payment.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">R</span>emember that flexibility when interviewing is considered a positive attribute.  Every effort will be made to accommodate your work schedule.  You, our client(s) and our consultants are all very busy, so the more flexible your schedule the better.\r\n\r\n<span class=\"moffitt-accent-letter\">Y</span>our resume does not need to be perfect for our purposes.  We do not require that you update your resume and prefer that you did not.  We will interview you regarding your current employment and place that information into our professional format that represents you in the best manner.\r\n\r\nTo learn more about how we search for candidates and our approach to our work, <a href=\"http://absdsgn.com/dev/moffitt/?page_id=15\">visit Our Process page</a>. \r\n','Candidates','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2018-12-28 23:52:13','2018-12-28 23:52:13','',13,'http://